    <lb n="31" type="worddiv"/>λαιον ἢ τὸ <app type="BL"><lem resp="1.93"><choice><corr>ἐνοφειληθησόμενον</corr><sic>εν<unclear>ο</unclear>φ<unclear>ιλ</unclear>ηθησομενον</sic></choice></lem><rdg>ἐν <choice><corr>ὀφειλῇ</corr><sic><unclear>ο</unclear>φ<unclear>ιλ</unclear>η</sic></choice> θησόμενον</rdg></app> 

